trans-unit.source: Represents the format to view an email message.
trans-unit.target: Representerer formatet for å vise en e-postmelding.

trans-unit.source: Use the AlternateView class to specify copies of an e-mail message in different formats.
trans-unit.target: Bruk klassen AlternateView til å angi kopier av en e-postmelding i forskjellige formater.

trans-unit.source: For example, if you send a message in HTML, you might also want provide a plain text version in case some of the recipients use e-mail readers that cannot display HTML content.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel hvis du sender en melding i HTML, kan du også angi en ren tekst-versjon i tilfelle noen av mottakerne bruker e-lesere som ikke kan vise HTML-innhold.

trans-unit.source: This class has two properties <xref:System.Net.Mail.AlternateView.LinkedResources%2A> and <xref:System.Net.Mail.AlternateView.BaseUri%2A> that are used to resolve URLs within the content of the email.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen har to egenskaper <xref:System.Net.Mail.AlternateView.LinkedResources%2A>og <xref:System.Net.Mail.AlternateView.BaseUri%2A>som brukes til å løse URL-adresser i innholdet i e-postmeldingen.</xref:System.Net.Mail.AlternateView.BaseUri%2A> </xref:System.Net.Mail.AlternateView.LinkedResources%2A>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Net.Mail.AlternateView.LinkedResources%2A> is a collection of <xref:System.Net.Mail.LinkedResource> objects.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Net.Mail.AlternateView.LinkedResources%2A>er en samling av <xref:System.Net.Mail.LinkedResource>objekter.</xref:System.Net.Mail.LinkedResource></xref:System.Net.Mail.AlternateView.LinkedResources%2A>

trans-unit.source: When rendered, URLs within the e-mail's content are first matched against the URLs in the <xref:System.Net.Mail.LinkedResource.ContentLink%2A> of each <xref:System.Net.Mail.LinkedResource> object in the <xref:System.Net.Mail.AlternateView.LinkedResources%2A> collection, and resolved.
trans-unit.target: Når den gjengis, URL-adresser på innholdet i e-posten sammenlignes først mot URL-adresser i de <xref:System.Net.Mail.LinkedResource.ContentLink%2A>for hver <xref:System.Net.Mail.LinkedResource>objekt i den <xref:System.Net.Mail.AlternateView.LinkedResources%2A>samling, og løst.</xref:System.Net.Mail.AlternateView.LinkedResources%2A> </xref:System.Net.Mail.LinkedResource> </xref:System.Net.Mail.LinkedResource.ContentLink%2A>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Net.Mail.AlternateView.BaseUri%2A> is used by the mail reader to resolve relative URLs within the body, and also to resolve relative <xref:System.Net.Mail.LinkedResource.ContentLink%2A> URLs, in the <xref:System.Net.Mail.AlternateView.LinkedResources%2A> collection.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Net.Mail.AlternateView.BaseUri%2A>brukes av e-leseren til å løse relative URL-adresser i meldingsteksten samt å ordne relativ <xref:System.Net.Mail.LinkedResource.ContentLink%2A>URL-adresser i de <xref:System.Net.Mail.AlternateView.LinkedResources%2A>samlingen.</xref:System.Net.Mail.AlternateView.LinkedResources%2A> </xref:System.Net.Mail.LinkedResource.ContentLink%2A></xref:System.Net.Mail.AlternateView.BaseUri%2A>

trans-unit.source: This method is called by the public `Dispose()` method and the <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden kalles av offentlig `Dispose()` metoden og <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>metode.</xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>

trans-unit.source: `Dispose()` invokes the protected `Dispose(Boolean)` method with the `disposing` parameter set to `true`.
trans-unit.target: `Dispose()`Aktiverer den beskyttede `Dispose(Boolean)` metoden med den `disposing` parameteren satt til `true`.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> invokes `Dispose` with `disposing` set to `false`.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>aktiverer `Dispose` med `disposing` satt til `false`.</xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>

trans-unit.source: When the `disposing` parameter is true, this method releases all resources held by any managed objects that this <xref:System.Net.Mail.AlternateView> references.
trans-unit.target: Når den `disposing` -parameteren er SANN, denne metoden Frigjør alle ressurser holdes av administrerte objekter som denne <xref:System.Net.Mail.AlternateView>referanser.</xref:System.Net.Mail.AlternateView>

trans-unit.source: This method invokes the `Dispose()` method of each referenced object.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden starter den `Dispose()` metode for hver referert objekt.
